graph TB
    User([User / App / API]) --> MCP_Client
    
    subgraph MCP [MCP — Universal Tool Protocol]
        MCP_Client[MCP Client<br/>Discovers + calls tools] --> MCP_Server1[MCP Server: DB<br/>search, read, write]
        MCP_Client --> MCP_Server2[MCP Server: APIs<br/>Slack, Drive, GitHub]
        MCP_Client --> MCP_Server3[MCP Server: Custom<br/>Your internal tools]
    end
    
    MCP_Client --> Gateway
    
    subgraph CompoundAI [Compound AI System]
        Gateway[LiteLLM Gateway<br/>Multi-provider + fallback]
        
        Gateway --> SemanticCache{Semantic Cache<br/>30-40% hit rate}
        SemanticCache -->|HIT| Response
        SemanticCache -->|MISS| Router
        
        Router[Complexity Router<br/>rules / classifier] -->|Simple 70%| CheapPath
        Router -->|Complex 30%| ExpensivePath
        Router -->|Multi-hop| GraphPath
        
        subgraph CheapPath [Simple Path — $0.001/query]
            BM25[BM25 Retriever<br/>FREE] --> Mini[GPT-4o-mini]
        end
        
        subgraph ExpensivePath [Complex Path — $0.03/query]
            Hybrid[Hybrid Search<br/>Dense + BM25 + RRF] --> Rerank[Reranker<br/>+10-20% precision]
            Rerank --> GPT4[GPT-4o]
        end
        
        subgraph GraphPath [Knowledge Graph Path]
            EntityQ[Entity Detection] --> Neo4j[(Neo4j Graph DB)]
            Neo4j --> Traverse[Multi-hop Traversal<br/>Bob → Alice → Carol]
            Traverse --> GPT4_G[GPT-4o + Graph Context]
        end
    end
    
    Mini --> Guardrails
    GPT4 --> Guardrails
    GPT4_G --> Guardrails
    
    subgraph Safety [Safety Layer]
        Guardrails[Input: Moderation + PII Redact + Injection Defense]
        Guardrails --> OutputCheck[Output: PII Scan + Faithfulness + Policy]
    end
    
    OutputCheck --> Response([Response])
    
    subgraph LLMOps [LLMOps Pipeline]
        direction TB
        PromptGit[Prompts in Git<br/>PR review] --> GoldenTest[Golden Dataset<br/>200+ tests]
        GoldenTest -->|Pass| CanaryDeploy[Canary 10%<br/>24h monitor]
        GoldenTest -->|Fail| Block[Block Deploy]
        CanaryDeploy -->|Healthy| FullDeploy[100% Rollout]
        CanaryDeploy -->|Degraded| Rollback[Instant Rollback]
    end
    
    subgraph Monitoring [Production Monitoring]
        Latency[Latency p50/p95/p99]
        Errors[Error Rate < 2%]
        Cost[Cost vs Budget]
        Faith[Faithfulness > 90%<br/>Weekly 1% sampling]
        Bias[Monthly Bias Audit]
    end
    
    Response --> Monitoring
    
    subgraph DataLayer [Data Architecture]
        VectorDB[(Qdrant<br/>Embeddings)]
        Postgres[(PostgreSQL<br/>Structured data)]
        S3[(S3 / MongoDB<br/>Raw documents)]
        
        subgraph EmbeddingPipeline [Embedding Pipeline]
            Extract[Extract] --> Chunk[Chunk<br/>Recursive + Parent-Child]
            Chunk --> Dedup[Dedup<br/>Content hash]
            Dedup --> EmbedStore[Embed + Store<br/>with metadata]
        end
        
        EmbedStore --> VectorDB
    end
    
    subgraph LocalLLM [Local / Edge Option]
        Ollama[Ollama<br/>ollama run llama3]
        LlamaCpp[llama.cpp<br/>CPU inference]
        MLX_Local[MLX<br/>Apple Silicon]
    end
    
    Gateway -.->|Privacy / offline<br/>/ development| LocalLLM
    
    subgraph Distillation [Model Optimization]
        Teacher[GPT-4 labels 10K examples<br/>$300] --> Student[Fine-tune Llama-8B<br/>$50]
        Student --> Quantize[Quantize to 4-bit<br/>100x cheaper than GPT-4]
        Quantize --> vLLM[Deploy via vLLM<br/>2-4x throughput]
    end
    
    subgraph MoE [Mixture of Experts]
        Mixtral[Mixtral 8x7B<br/>47B knowledge<br/>13B compute per token<br/>Best self-hosting value]
    end
    
    vLLM --> Gateway
    Mixtral --> Gateway

    style Gateway fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style SemanticCache fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style Router fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style Guardrails fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Response fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style MCP_Client fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style FullDeploy fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style Block fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Faith fill:#da3633,color:#fff
